In [ ]:
import numpy as np

def fit_and_score_features(X, y):
    n_features = X.shape[1]
    scores = np.empty(n_features)
    m = CoxPHSurvivalAnalysis()
    for j in range(n_features):
        Xj = X[:, j:j+1]
        m.fit(Xj, y)
        scores[j] = m.score(Xj, y)
    return scores

scores = fit_and_score_features(surv_features_train.values, surv_labels_train)
pd.Series(scores, index=surv_features_train.columns).sort_values(ascending=False)
